Name:         BisectFromOasis
Version:      0
Synopsis:     Demonstrate how to (optioanlly) implement bisect coverage
Authors:      Leonid Rozenberg <leonidr@gmail.com>
License:      LGPL with OCaml linking exception

OASISFormat:  0.4
BuildTools:   ocamlbuild
Plugins:      META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)
XDevFilesEnableConfigure: false

Flag coverage
  Description: Instrument code with Bisect to provide coverage reports
  Default:     false

Executable helloworld
  Path: .
  MainIs: main.ml
  CompiledObject: best

Library greeter
  Path: src
  Modules: Greeter

Executable helloworld_lib
  Path: .
  BuildDepends: greeter
  MainIs: main_lib.ml
  CompiledObject: best
